 215:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/../misc/lv_text_private.h **** /**
 216:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/../misc/lv_text_private.h ****  * Test if character can be treated as marker, and don't need to be rendered.
 217:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/../misc/lv_text_private.h ****  * Note, this is not a full list. Add your findings to the list.
 218:Drivers/lvgl/src/draw/../misc/lv_text_private.h ****  *
